Changes in version 0.7


* multiple viewports now supported (one per camera) 
* main loop control is now via Exceptions
* engine timing control is now in a TimeKeeper class instance
* engines 'idle' method can be method or generator-method
* support modules now named consistently *_objects
* stereoscopic module rewritten to use 'wrapper' design pattern
* new stereoscopic demos added, for both edimensional LCD 
  glasses and red/blue glasses
* tests (unittest based) added
* documentation upgraded - still epydoc, but more overview
* various bugfixes, mostly from testing; pychecker checked
* library re-organized, with demos and tests in subdirs; demos
  will run without installing module
